{"tid":626780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奇異博士赴韓 合掌鞠躬被指歧視韓國人","createTime":"2018-04-12T11:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T12:47:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9a088f9adc7e9cabe3cb61f8a864e385dadf66","tid":626780,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180412/640_7b070b360ac8811b46157f0f752b4753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180412%2F640_7b070b360ac8811b46157f0f752b4753.jpg&h=2c513b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n英國男星「奇異博士」班奈狄克康柏拜區在首爾仁川機場鞠躬合掌意外引發網友不滿。</span><br />\n<br />\n漫威超級英雄大片《復仇者聯盟：無限之戰》即將於25日在台上映，該片的超級英雄們已開始分工跑宣傳，「奇異博士」班奈狄克康柏拜區（Benedict Cumberbatch）、「邪神洛基」湯姆希德斯頓與「蜘蛛人」湯姆霍蘭德這幾天先到韓國首爾打片，大明星們在機場就引起不少騷動。但是沒想到班奈狄克在機場弓著身子合掌打招呼的動作，意外惹來韓國網友不滿，認為他想攏絡人心卻沒入境隨俗做功課，有網友開罵「韓國沒這種打招呼方式」，還扣了一個「歧視」的大帽子給他，電影公司不得不回應，他的姿勢是因為他信奉佛教。<br />\n<br />\n首爾近來已成為亞洲重要宣傳大站，《復仇者3》的亞洲宣傳首站就選定首爾，接下來會到新加坡、上海。但沒想到好感度超高的班奈狄克到了首爾，卻因無心的舉動被罵，還有網友拿他與不久前剛造訪的凱蒂佩芮相比較，認為凱蒂學韓文並比手指愛心，比起他有誠意許多。（李子凡／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180412/1333080/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180412%2F1333080%2F&d=ASUwK%2Bpx0BiGpEbkl%2FvLzttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=3abddc9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180412%2F1333080%2F&h=eeebb27f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180412/1333080/</a>"},{"pid":"7e09d6d032b9cba89b084d2adc262ef2d740e936","tid":626780,"uid":93986,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"這點小事都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話大陸人跖街就話姐"},{"pid":"a682daadcc4d14d31b7adb22de5f666c4c02a745","tid":626780,"uid":141151,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"要俾手指愛心先算尊重韓國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb34ae73e126f95e2d390e963809affd35b6157","tid":626780,"uid":138658,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"韓狗真係特撚別麻煩<br />\n洗唔洗跪埋係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6dd1aa50cccee2ecacec80905bab6f691a2967","tid":626780,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"揾左咁多年<br />\n終於揾到個國家仲on9 過蝗國同台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5cbf79b0980378a5c28385c49d45a58d3a0aaf","tid":626780,"uid":30800,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3a6dd1aa50cccee2ecacec80905bab6f691a2967","tid":626780,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"揾左咁多年<br />\n終於揾到個國家仲on9 過蝗國同台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔係咁講丫，三個地方都係咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff6c296fe9a7992aaa990069882877e6abae234","tid":626780,"uid":26611,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"要幾自卑先講得出依啲說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b8b8a9ba7a609663a07685c713670ad95e8e58","tid":626780,"uid":2545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fb5cbf79b0980378a5c28385c49d45a58d3a0aaf","tid":